additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. If pain or irritation persists for more than 48 hours - consult your doctor. The presence of blood in the urine warrants immediate medical attention. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. This product is suitable for consumption during Pregnancy and Breastfeeding. We recommend consulting your Primary Healthcare Professional when considering changes to your supplementary routine, particularly during Pregnancy and Breastfeeding, so that your situation can be monitored as necessary.
